Definition: Given an input stream, the objective of this task is to create an output stream with grammatically incorrect words substituted by a slot ('_') so that these words can be corrected. The input is a stream of words and the output is also a stream of words with every grammatically incorrect word in the stream substituted by a slot ('_') character.
